Gazit-Globe Advances as Second-Quarter Profit Increases 68%

-- B y   S u s a n   L e r n e r
-- 
2011-08-22T14:29:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/gazit-globe-gains-most-in-a-week-as-second-quarter-profit-climbs.html
Gazit-Globe Ltd. (GLOB)  rose for the first
time in three days after the Tel-Aviv-based real-estate investor
reported a 68 percent increase in second-quarter profit.  The shares increased 1.1 percent to 37.16 shekels at the
4:30 p.m. close in  Tel Aviv , after earlier climbing as much as
2.8 percent.  Net income increased to 251 million shekels ($70 million)
from 149 million shekels a year earlier, the Tel Aviv-based
company said today in an e-mailed statement. Funds from
operations climbed 19 percent to 95 million shekels, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Susan Lerner in Jerusalem at 
